================================================================================
COMMERCIAL LICENSE OPTIONS
================================================================================

Choose what fits your use. You know your situation best.

PRICING (per seat — one license per team member):

  Annual        $99 / seat / year
  Perpetual     $299 / seat — one-time purchase

EXAMPLES:

  Solo developer                    →  1 seat × Annual ($99/year)
  5-person studio                   →  5 seats × Annual ($495/year)
  Team of 10, long-term investment  →  10 seats × Perpetual ($2,990)

To purchase: https://signalcompose.gumroad.com/l/maxmcp1year
Custom terms or questions: licensing@signalcompose.com

We are happy to talk. This is a relationship, not a transaction.

================================================================================
ACADEMIC USE
================================================================================

Academic use is free.

You qualify for free use if you are:
- A student enrolled at an accredited educational institution
- A faculty member, teacher, or researcher at an accredited institution
- Using the software solely for educational or non-commercial research

If you are unsure whether you qualify, contact us at: licensing@signalcompose.com

All other use — including commercial, professional, or organizational use —
requires a commercial license.

================================================================================
ABOUT SUPPORT AND MAINTENANCE
================================================================================

This software is provided as-is. We do not offer formal support as part of this
license.

That said: we do maintain this software. We read feedback, fix bugs, and care
about what we build. We simply cannot guarantee timelines or responses.

If you need a formal support agreement, reach out: licensing@signalcompose.com

Contributions are welcome. Bug reports are appreciated.
This is a community, and your voice matters.

